description: This file is the entry point for a React application. It imports React libraries, CSS styles, and the main App component. It creates a React root and renders the App component within React.StrictMode, attaching it to the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the React component tree.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the root.
